OL,3,CNo extra money for NHS and teacher pay
OL,4,Crises, says No 10, amid strikes warning
OL,6,FThe government will have tough choices
OL,7,Fto make if it wants to avoid more
OL,8,Findustrial action and disruption, as
OL,9,FITV News Political Correspondent
OL,10,FShehab Khan reports
OL,12,FThere will be no further funding to
OL,13,Fmeet pay increases for teachers and
OL,14,FNHS staff, if they exceed the
OL,15,Fgovernment's spending budgets, Downing
OL,16,FStreet has said, as unions warn of
OL,17,Ffurther industrial action.
