OL,3,CNo extra money for NHS and teacher pay
OL,4,Crises, says No 10, amid strikes warning
OL,6,FHe told ITV News: "We accepted the pay
OL,7,Frecommendation last year, we were able
OL,8,Fto settle those disputes. Nobody
OL,9,Fwanted our nurses and doctors in
OL,10,Findustrial disputes.
OL,12,F"The pay review bodies are now going
OL,13,Fthrough the process making their
OL,14,Frecommendations and we'll consider
OL,15,Fthem as we always do, that's part of
OL,16,Fthe annual cycle."
OL,18,FAsked if he accepts that any rejection
OL,19,Fof pay rises could lead to further
OL,20,Fwalkouts, the PM said: "Well I don't
OL,21,Fthink anybody wants to see strikes.
