OL,3,CNo extra money for NHS and teacher pay
OL,4,Crises, says No 10, amid strikes warning
OL,6,F"Doctors and nurses don't want to be
OL,7,Fon strike, patients don't want to see
OL,8,Fstrikes, so obviously we want to do as
OL,9,Fwe're doing now which is work with NHS
OL,10,Fstaff, not pit against them which the
OL,11,Flast government did."
OL,13,FBut Downing Street was clear on Monday
OL,14,Fthat the government would not be
OL,15,Fproviding any extra funding for
OL,16,Fincreases above 2.8%.
