OL,3,CNo extra money for NHS and teacher pay
OL,4,Crises, says No 10, amid strikes warning
OL,6,FGeneral Secretary of the National
OL,7,FEducation Union, Daniel Kebede, told
OL,8,FITV News: "I appreciate the government
OL,9,Fhave tough decisions to make, but
OL,10,Fwhilst there was a pay award last year
OL,11,Fthat was accepted by the profession,
OL,12,F14 years of Conservative Government
OL,13,Fsaw pay freezes and pay cuts and has,
OL,14,Fquite frankly, brought the system to
OL,15,Fthe brink of crisis."
OL,17,FHe added: "No one wants to take strike
OL,18,Faction but of course as a trade union
OL,19,Fwe do stand ready to act industrially
OL,20,Fif we need to."
