OL,6,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies' Paul
OL,7,FJohnson said: "As ever, the
OL,8,Fgovernment's got choices about if it's
OL,9,Fincreasing pay, it can either pay less
OL,10,Fon other things - maybe less in the
OL,11,Fway of public services - or it'll have
OL,12,Fto increase taxes to pay for them.
OL,14,F"Those are the choices that you always
OL,15,Fhave. There's certainly no room to
OL,16,Fincrease pay and do all the things the
